# Optional. Published Google Sheet as CSV (first column = Yahoo tickers, one per row).
# In Google Sheets: File → Share → Publish to web → publish the sheet, then use the
# link and add &output=csv or use the CSV export URL from the published doc.
# Dev server proxies this URL at /api/watchlist-csv to avoid CORS.
# Vercel: set the same name under Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# (Production / Preview). Redeploy after changing it — Vite inlines VITE_* at build time.
# VITE_WATCHLIST_CSV_URL=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/XXXXXXXX/pub?output=csv
